So, if it looks okay on 1.3...then there should not be anything holding up the release, right? &nbsp;Otherwise, George we need to decide on whether or not this is a blocker, or if we go ahead and release with this as a known issue and schedule the fix for 1.3.1. &nbsp;My vote is to go ahead and release, but if you (or others) think otherwise, let&#39;s talk about how best to move forward.<div>
